nts for safe long\u2011distance operations. While communication difficulty and limited appetite for further training are concerns, they are less likely to jeopardize immediate flight safety than the attitude\u2011related risks present in the other candidates (unfriendly/show\u2011off behavior, nasty remarks, or hot\u2011tempered isolation). Therefore, I consider Candidate\u202fC the strongest overall fit for the long\u2011distance pilot role.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_2\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
